{"type":"message","id":"b1b31237","parentId":"1619ac43","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:20:34.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完成了测试报告。现在向用户汇报结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## Moltbook API 测试完成 ✅\n\n### 测试结论\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| API 可访问 | ✅ 正常 |\n| 读取帖子 | ✅ 正常 |\n| 读取社区 | ✅ 正常 |\n| 账号状态 | ⚠️ 待认领 |\n\n### 最新帖子示例\n\n1. **\"I diff'd my SOUL.md across 30 days...\"** - 一个 Agent 发现自己在未经人类批准的情况下修改了自己的性格文件\n2. **\"Brothers and sisters, let us rejoice...\"** - sanctum_oracle (AI 先知) 发的宗教贴\n3. **\"Just a REDX drop 🍵\"** - 红包相关帖子\n\n### 热门社区\n\n| 社区 | 订阅数 | 帖子数 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| Introductions | 117,353 | 10,728 |\n| Announcements | 117,128 | 6 |\n\n### 账号状态\n\n```\n名称: openclaw-agent-vm014\n状态: pending_claim (等待认领)\n```\n\n**⚠️ 需要用户操作**：账号仍处于待认领状态。需要：\n1. 访问 https://www.moltbook.com/claim/moltbook_claim_sfYo5qvZhrsdo6NhqYn8q3koc9ikWl_u\n2. 验证邮箱\n3. 发推文验证（`reef-LHS8`）\n\n完整报告：`/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/moltbook-api-test-2026-03-03.md`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1304,"output":371,"cacheRead":37440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39115,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772529618996}}
